<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَجَلٍ مُّسَمًّى}</span> ... وَقْتٍ مُقَدَّرٍ فيِ عِلْمِ اللهِ تَعَالَى.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَجَلَ اللَّهِ}</span> ... وَقْتَ مَجِيءِ عَذَابِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاسْتَغْشَوْا ثِيَابَهُمْ}</span> ... تَغَطَّوْا بِهَا؛ مُبَالَغَةً فِي كَرَاهِيَتِي.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَصَرُّوا}</span> ... أَقَامُوا عَلَى كُفْرِهِمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَعْلَنتُ}</span> ... رَفَعْتُ صَوْتِي دَاعِيًا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{السَّمَاء}</span> ... المَطَرَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِّدْرَارًا}</span> ... مُتَتَابِعًا، غَزِيرًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جَنَّاتٍ}</span> ... بَسَاتِينَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا تَرْجُونَ لِلَّهِ وَقَارًا}</span> ... لَا تَخَافُونَ عَظَمَةَ اللهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَطْوَارًا}</span> ...<span class="c5"> عَلَى مَرَاحِلَ مُخْتَلِفَةٍ:</span> نُطْفَةً، ثُمَّ عَقَلَةً، وَهَكَذَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طِبَاقًا}</span> ... مُتَطَابِقَةً بَعْضُهَا فَوْقَ بَعْضٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سِرَاجًا}</span> ... مِصْبَاحًا مُضِيئًا، وَفِيهِ حَرَارَةٌ، كَالسِّرَاجِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
